    + #underline[*Regularity*]: every letter is given a regular and predictable name.
    + #underline[*Completeness*]: letters used in any variety are included.
    + #underline[*Accuracy*]: as much as possible, the letter's name is an accurate representation of its sound.
    + #underline[*Unification of sound*]: the alphabet does not split a single sound into a digraph.
